data.description: This is an amazing house! Over 4000 sq.ft. finished on 3 levels & space to spread out! Updated kitchen granite, stainless appliances, new flooring, light fixtures, & more! Multiple work at home options including a library w/wall of built in cabinets, formal dining room, bedrooms, and the finished lower level. Upgrades include crown molding, skylights, pocket french doors, speaker system, 2 fireplaces, and geothermal heating and cooling (low bills!). The yard is one of the best w/composite deck, direct gas line for grill, extensive landscaping, & mature trees. The lower level offers a bonus room with walk out that could be used for a work out room, art studio/craft room, workshop or even another bedroom! Community pool & playground to enjoy in one of Muscatine's favorite neighborhoods
